<p>Is Bella wishing he'd been The Bachelor instead? Bella Varelis grinned as she happily chatted with hunky Studio 10 presenter Tristan MacManus on Friday in Sydney after getting dumped by Locky Gilbert </p>

<p>Unfortunately for Bella, however, the Irish TV star has been happily married to former actress Tahyna Tozzi for six years, and they have two young children together. </p>

<p>Bella couldn't wipe the smile off her face as she chatted with Tristan in between takes of the morning talk show.</p>

<p>Wearing a pale blue floral print cropped shirt, which sat off her shoulders and was knotted at her waist, Bella basked in the sunshine as she talked with the TV host.</p>

