<p>Standing alongside Tristan in a pair of strappy nude coloured stilettos, Bella listened intently as he spoke to her.</p>

<p>The newly-appointed Studio 10 host looked suave in a charcoal grey suit, which he paired with a white shirt, which he wore open at the collar.</p>

